{"type": "article", "id": 28635, "title": "复古灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-24T06:50:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145534Oft7JlHNYy5UpvdP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>设计工作室 <a href=\"http://plumen.com/\">Plumen</a> 最近与 <a href=\"Made.comhttp://www.made.com/\">Made.com</a> 再次合作，从 1950 年代的工作灯中汲取灵感，推出了 Memoir 系列灯具。这一系列包括了吊灯、台灯以及壁灯，配备的是 Plumen 002 LED 灯泡以及金属的网纱灯罩，昏黄的灯光从空隙中扩散开来，营造出朦胧的氛围。黑金金属与黄铜的搭配看上去非常典雅，有着浓浓的复古感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021455327QuBH8SjIWizD1JC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.84722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214553286vLCD35dJh4Nqi2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145533VpdZLJQoF90qSvbB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021455336HEkZNBl8uIYRGvL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}